Commit Message: Initial commit

asciicast2movie 0.1.1: render_asciicast_frames

Separation of render_asciicast_frames function from asciicast2video function.
render_asciicast_frames() renders list of asciicast using provided pyte
screen and stream. This can be useful for rendering one (continuous)
terminal session into multiple video clips.

Add upload Makefile target.
bug fix: ascicast timestamp start from 0.0
